WEBVTT

31:48.110 --> 31:48.800 line:80%
Like you.

31:49.720 --> 31:51.390 line:80%
Both parents dead since childhood,

31:51.390 --> 31:53.240 line:80%
with no one to rely on in this life.

31:53.240 --> 31:54.910 line:80%
No matter how beautiful jade is,

31:54.910 --> 31:57.040 line:80%
it's not as valuable as gold or silver.
